fi.explorator
Class Grid

java.lang.Object
  fi.explorator.Grid

public class Grid
extends java.lang.Object

2D grid which represents the area where the starting point and ending point of the path resides. This is the main composite object which holds the Cell and Edge instances. This works as data transfer object between visualization layer and path finding algorithms.
